tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE OfficeHours (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    day_of_week VARCHAR(20),
    start_time TIME,
    end_time TIME
)

CREATE TABLE virtual_office_hours (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    day_of_week VARCHAR(10),
    start_time TIME,
    end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE tutoring_sessions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    tutor_id INT,
    student_id INT,
    subject VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    session_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Virtual_Office_Hours (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    day_of_week VARCHAR(10),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Tutoring_Sessions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    tutor_id INT,
    subject VARCHAR(50),
    session_date DATE,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Student_Availability (
    student_id INT,
    day_of_week VARCHAR(10),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (student_id, day_of_week)
);

CREATE TABLE VirtualOfficeHours (
	office_hour_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	office_hour_date DATE,
	office_hour_start_time TIME,
	office_hour_end_time TIME,
	tutor_id INT,
	student_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE virtual_office_hours (
	office_hour_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	tutor_id INT,
	start_time TIMESTAMP,
	end_time TIMESTAMP,
)

CREATE TABLE tutoring_sessions (
	session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	tutor_id INT,
	student_id INT,
	start_time TIMESTAMP,
	end_time TIMESTAMP,
)

CREATE TABLE student_availability (
	student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	day_of_week VARCHAR(10),
	start_time TIMESTAMP,
	end_time TIMESTAMP,
)

CREATE TABLE student_preferences (
	student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	preferred_tutor_id INT,
	preferred_day VARCHAR(10),
	max_sessions_per_week INT,
)

CREATE TABLE tutor_availability (
	tutor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	day_of_week VARCHAR(10),
	start_time TIMESTAMP,
	end_time TIMESTAMP,
)
